data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.875% Interest Rate for those who qualify!!!! THIS IS IT!! A gorgeous reverse story and a half in Creekmoor of Westbrook. Main level living at its finest! 3-bedroom, 3.5 baths and a 3 car garage.  Could easily be a 4 bedroom with minimal effort.   This home is positioned beautifully in the heart of Creekmoor overlooking the golf course (#6 tee box). It is set-up perfectly for entertaining with a spacious kitchen, living area, and dining area! Plus, you have a nice deck view of the sunsets as well as watching the golfers tee off and head down the fairway.  A lower level that is fully finished and has great spaces (2 living areas, 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms), new flooring, new interior paint and meticulous maintenance make this property an incredible value.  Come see this gorgeous property today!
